{"tid":677109,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"初中中史歷史修訂課綱出爐　香港史不再為獨立課題　六四、六七不見影","createTime":"2018-05-25T02:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-25T02:42:52.000Z","uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"4619bf2a6ad83fcf0d2659a6765d086c0d18d34a","tid":677109,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:13:49.000Z","msg":"初中中史和歷史科課程修訂大綱今天出爐，第一階段和第二階段諮詢課綱都將香港史以獨立課題教授，但修訂課綱將香港史融入不同的中史課題，不再以獨立課題呈現。<br />\n<br />\n教育局表示，課程大綱最快將於2020學年在全港中一級開始逐級實施，但歡迎學校提早教。<br />\n<br />\n與第二階段諮詢稿相比，修訂課綱沒有將中國歷史上各時期的香港史列為獨立課題，而是融入在各中史課題中，如「清末至民國時期的香港」本是獨立課題，但取而代之的是在「國共合作與分裂」此課題中加入「1920年代內地與香港的關係」作為香港史。<br />\n<br />\n制訂課綱的委員會主席梁元生表示，在聆聽前線教師要求下，決定以「浸淫」方式教授香港史部分，而這科是中史，故希望在中史框架下看香港，「教學法不同，但目標都一樣，就是結合一起後講授給學生」。<br />\n<br />\n另外，六四事件和六七暴動等議題仍沒有納入課綱；在第二輪諮詢稿提到可教授的革命運動、省港大罷工等，這些字眼亦沒在修訂課綱中出現。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180524/s00001/1527154498966\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180524%2Fs00001%2F1527154498966&d=IzNnsw2NHj6Y0EKC5Yge5aS6uTmBE%2FuUnOR61Sj848o%3D&h=8d2bf117\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20180524%2Fs00001%2F1527154498966&h=82b9fe2d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20180524/s00001/1527154498966</a>"},{"pid":"32bb883fd13f9ce7a4821dcfde382fab5dcdc172","tid":677109,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"一直都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但學校會自己教"},{"pid":"4ee0b481b5d98042bda926ac814d7735f52748f0","tid":677109,"uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32bb883fd13f9ce7a4821dcfde382fab5dcdc172","tid":677109,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"一直都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但學校會自己教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"以前history有香港史，教鄧文廖侯彭個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0c9a41663498128a3321865e62a9a8b1d78d5384","tid":677109,"uid":34410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"4ee0b481b5d98042bda926ac814d7735f52748f0","tid":677109,"uid":38671,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"32bb883fd13f9ce7a4821dcfde382fab5dcdc172","tid":677109,"uid":103230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:14:58.000Z","msg":"一直都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但學校會自己教"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:16:42.000Z","msg":"以前history有香港史，教鄧文廖侯彭個d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-25T02:42:52.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  不過佢依個係中史課程<br />\n連六七暴動都唔講 不如民革 三反五反 大躍進都唔好講<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反正中國都係贏家既歷史"}]}